Lemaitre Vascular
	Provider of innovative devices for the treatment of peripheral vascular disease. The company\'s products include EndoFit Thoracic Stent Graft used for the repair of thoracic aortic aneurysm and dissection, UniFit Abdominal Stent Graft for abdominal aortic aneurysm, VascuTape Radiopaque Tape for the improvement of endovascular procedures, and AnastoClip Vessel Closure System for the attachment of blood vessels, primarily for dialysis access. It\'s product portfolio also comprises of LeMaitre Balloon Catheters for the removal of blood clots, occlusion, and facilitation of blood flow, Reddick Cholangiogram Catheter for the introduction of dye into the cystic duct, and OptiLock Implantable Port, a central venous infusion of drugs and nutrients.
